16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
18 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 24-162 of Title 70, unless there
19 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
20 A. This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Federal
21 Education Guidance Disclosure Act".
22 B. Within five (5) days of receiving a guidance document from
23 the United States Department of Education, the State Department of
24 Education shall publish the guidance document on an Internet website
